description: '### Testing framework: add support for loading files with global constants\nA
  new function `Test.register_file_constants` is introduced. It takes a string (file
  path) and returns a list of strings corresponding to the hashes of the registered
  constants.\n\nThe file format is the same as the used in `--file-constants` for
  sub-command `compile contract`.'
